[[芝加哥|芝加哥]][[市长|市长]][[李察·米高·戴利|李察·米高·戴利]]在2006年5月15日把塑像面世那天訂为「云门日」。卡普尔参加了庆祝典礼，[[爵士乐|爵士乐]][[小号|小号]]手及领队奥尔博·戴维斯（Orbert Davis）和芝加哥爵士交响乐团並在典礼上演奏了由戴维斯创作的「为云门吹奏（Fanfare for Cloud Gate）」。<ref name="CGD">{{Cite web|url=http://audio.wbez.org/848/2006/05/848_20060515b.mp3|title=Cloud Gate Day|date=2006-06-15|work=Chicago Public Radio|accessdate=2008-05-02|author=Lifson, Edward|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080910135209/http://audio.wbez.org/848/2006/05/848_20060515b.mp3|archivedate=2008-09-10}}</ref>公众从不一样的出发点看塑像，并亲切地称它为「豆荚」。<ref name="AMPAPaNYI">{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2006/08/20/arts/design/20kenn.html|title=A Most Public Artist Polishes a New York Image|accessdate=2008-06-02|date=2006-08-20|publisher=The New York Times Company|work=The New York Times|author=Kennedy, Randy|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308123408/https://www.nytimes.com/2006/08/20/arts/design/20kenn.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>「雲門」成为了一个很受欢迎的公众艺术品，<ref name="AKPPF" /><ref name="SaM">{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/05/30/arts/design/30kapo.html|title=Sculptor as Magician|accessdate=2008-06-03|date=2008-05-30|publisher=The New York Times Company|work=The New York Times|author=Smith, Roberta|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308162059/https://www.nytimes.com/2008/05/30/arts/design/30kapo.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>并成为了[[明信片|明信片]]、[[运动衫|运动衫]]和[[海报|海报]]等[[纪念品|纪念品]]上的必备之物。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?file=/chronicle/archive/2006/07/30/TRGPUK5SDH1.DTL|title=Chicago's architectural razzmatazz: New or old, skyscrapers reflect city's brash and playful character|accessdate=2008-07-31|date=2006-07-30|publisher=Hearst Communications Inc.|work=San Francisco Chronicle|author=King, John|archive-date=2009-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090306172529/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?file=%2Fchronicle%2Farchive%2F2006%2F07%2F30%2FTRGPUK5SDH1.DTL|dead-url=no}}</ref>塑像吸引了很多的市民，以及来自世界各地的游客和艺术爱好者。<ref name="TWAM2-3">{{cite news|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/05/25/arts/25weekahead.html|title=The Week Ahead: May 25–31|accessdate=2008-06-02|date=2008-05-25|publisher=The New York Times Company|work=The New York Times|author=Kennedy, Randy|archive-date=2021-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210417021005/https://www.nytimes.com/2008/05/25/arts/25weekahead.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>它是卡普尔众多艺术品中最为人知的一件。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,1594123,00.html|title=Thinking Way Out of the Box|accessdate=2008-07-07|date=2007-02-27|publisher=Time Inc.|work=Time|author=Lacayo, Richard|archive-date=2012-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120416052246/http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,1594123,00.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

《[[时代_(杂志)|时代]]》杂志称该塑像为游客合影留恋的必去之地，作爲一个艺术品来说，这更是一个大師級作品。<ref name="AKPPF" />时代杂志还把该塑像形容爲「游客[[磁铁|磁铁]]」和「非凡的艺术品」，<ref name="TWAM2-3" /><ref>{{cite news|url=http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9806EED71E3BF930A25754C0A9629C8B63|title=Letter From Chicago; A Prized Project, a Mayor and Persistent Criticism|accessdate=2008-07-30|date=2004-07-13|author=Kinzer, Stephen|publisher=The New York Times Company|work=The New York Times|archive-date=2009-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090307053618/http://query.nytimes.com/gst/fullpage.html?res=9806EED71E3BF930A25754C0A9629C8B63|dead-url=no}}</ref>而《[[今日美国|今日美国]]》则認爲其堪称为「[[抽象派|抽象派]]的不朽作品」。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/USAToday/access/687931411.html?dids=687931411:687931411&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&date=Sep+3%2C+2004&author=&pub=USA+TODAY&edition=&startpage=D.08&desc=What+have+artists+wrought+from+9%2F11%3F|title=What have artists wrought from 9/11?|accessdate=2008-07-31|date=2004-09-03|work=[[USA_Today|USA Today]]|archive-date=2012-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121025104328/http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/USAToday/access/687931411.html?dids=687931411:687931411&FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&date=Sep+3,+2004&author=&pub=USA+TODAY&edition=&startpage=D.08&desc=What+have+artists+wrought+from+9%2F11%3F|dead-url=no}}</ref>芝加哥艺术评论员爱德华·利弗森（Edward Lifson） 认为「云门」是世界上最好的公众艺术品之一。<ref name="CGD" />美国焊接工程协会则向MTH实业公司和性能结构公司颁发了「非凡接焊大奖」。<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.usgnn.com/newsAWS20071002.htm|title=AWS Honors MTH and Others for Work on Cloud Gate Project|publisher=Key Communications, Inc./The USGlass News Network|work=USGlass Magazine|accessdate=2008-06-02|archive-date=2008-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080116064234/http://www.usgnn.com/newsAWS20071002.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>时代杂志也把千禧公园命名为2004年十大建筑成就之一，称「云门」是公园里的主要景点之一。<ref name="TBA">{{cite news|url=http://www.time.com/time/bestandworst/2004/arch.html |title=The Best Architecture |accessdate=2008-06-03 |publisher=Time Inc. |work=Time |author=Lacayo, Richard |date=2004-12-18 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080510154129/http://www.time.com/time/bestandworst/2004/arch.html |archivedate=2008-05-10 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

